{"tid":2349313,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[Viu到完場勿劇透] 2020年度叱咤樂壇流行榜頒獎典禮（6）","createTime":"2021-01-01T12:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T12:49:33.000Z","uid":206668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"042ee393c5ebb1649589165025b085a0927aa597","tid":2349313,"uid":206668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:45:16.000Z","msg":"2020年度叱咤樂壇流行榜頒獎典禮，是由香港商業電台舉辦的一個本地音樂頒獎典禮，將於<strong><ins>2021年1月1日晚上7時</ins></strong>於九龍灣國際展貿中心舉行，本屆頒獎禮雖恢復為實體形式，但將不設現場觀眾，以保持2019冠狀病毒病疫情期間的社交距離。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R8EF8fk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR8EF8fk.png&h=fcdd18f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本屆主題定為「一切從音樂再開始」，美術主題為一輛叱咤火炬形狀的飛船在火星中準備起飛，帶領大家再次踏上奇妙的音樂之旅， 寓意誠邀大家一同登上飛船、重新向未知的將來出發。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>直播及轉播：</ins><br />\n叱咤903&mdash;聲音直播<br />\n<a href=\"http://my903.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmy903.com&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=db2e5459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://my903.com</a>、<a href=\"http://881903.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F881903.com&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=941a5488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://881903.com</a>&mdash;網上串流視像直播<br />\n手機程式 Hong Kong Toolbar（Android 用戶）、商台節目重溫 app / Hong Kong Toolbar（iOS用戶）&mdash;影片直播<br />\nViuTV&mdash;影片轉播<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>此post為ViuTV區，網上live post請移玉步</strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>劇透撚仆街死啦</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d510d23178b7876f71e3b0c2b3927023426abc55","tid":2349313,"uid":155720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:45:43.000Z","msg":"唔洗用力唱歌"},{"pid":"77bfbd7ce3fbbf63edde57cc780657b888344d4b","tid":2349313,"uid":7079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:45:47.000Z","msg":"支咪唔同左<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b3